    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid-running driver with good bones and plenty of usable life left. Starts, idles, and moves out well, with a drivetrain that feels stout and a chassis that still tracks confidently. Not a showpiece, but a great budget buy for someone who wants dependable transportation, a shop truck, or a project platform with real potential. Recent upkeep and a straightforward mechanical layout make it an appealing candidate for someone who appreciates function over cosmetics. Priced to reflect its rough condition while still offering strong value for a running, usable vehicle.",
